sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant API as Control Plane API
  participant P as Policy Service
  participant S as Session Service
  participant W as Workflow Engine
  participant R as Runtime Orchestrator
  participant E as Sandboxed Executor
  participant M as Model Gateway
  participant T as Tool Gateway
  participant A as Artifact Service
  participant O as Observability

  U->>API: POST /v1/sessions
  API->>P: Authorize launch and classify input
  P-->>API: Allow with policy context
  API->>S: Create session
  S->>W: Start durable workflow
  W->>R: Schedule runtime
  R->>E: Start executor with scoped context
  E->>M: Invoke model through gateway
  M-->>E: Model response and usage
  E->>T: Invoke approved tools
  T-->>E: Tool result
  E->>A: Write artifact version
  A-->>E: Artifact reference
  E->>S: Report turn and output
  S->>O: Emit events, logs, traces, cost
  S-->>API: Session updated
  API-->>U: Live event stream and final artifact
